  "notes": "Ecruteak City is the cultural heart of Johto. It sits between Route 37 (south), Route 38 (west), and Route 42 (east). The city features the Burned Tower ruins to the northwest and the Bell Tower / Tin Tower to the northeast. The legendary beasts (Raikou, Entei, Suicune) event triggers in the Burned Tower basement. The Fog Badge enables Surf outside of battle and makes Pokemon up to Lv50 obey. The city fly-point is registered on first visit via EcruteakCityFlypointCallback."
